quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,56,"Ubwami bw’uwo musi buzoba ari ubw’Imana yonyene gusa ari nayo izocira urubanza ruri hagati yabo, rero bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikogwa vyiza, bazoba bari mumirima myiza ifise imigisha ntangere"
  22,57,Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri nuguhakana amajambo yacu matagatifu abo bantu bazoronka ibihano bibatetereza
  22,58,"Nabamwe bimutse kubera idini ry’Imana hanyuma bakicwa canke bagasandaba, ntankeka Imana izobahemba, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nziza isasagaza imigisha yayo kuri bose"
  22,59,Izobinjiza ahantu bazo kwishima bonyene kandi ntankeka niyo ifise ubumenyi kandi niyo ntore
  22,60,"Uku niko bimeze kuwihora nkuko yabigiriwe, hanyuma agahemukirwa ntankeka Imana izomufasha mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise ikigongwe n’impuhwe nyinshi zihagije"
  22,61,"Ibi vyose nukubera yuko Imana yinjiza Ijoro Mumutaga, nukwinjiza Umutaga mw’Ijoro, kandi Imana niyo yumva nukubona"
  22,62,"Ivyo vyose nukubera yuko Imana iriho, nabarya basenga ibintazi ivyo bintu ntashingiro bifise n’Imana niyo iri hejuru y’ibintu vyose kandi niyo nkuru"
  22,63,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana imanura amazi avuye mubicu hanyuma Isi nayo igaca ihinduka ikaba urwatsi rutoto, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyinyegeje nibiri k’umugaragaro"
  22,64,"Nivyiwe wenyene mubiri Mumajuru yose n’ibiri kw’Isi vyose mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene amatungo yose, hamwe n’ihayagizwa ryose niryo rimukwiriye"